                        <h2>About us</h2>
                        <p>At Duvee Technology, we are passionate about transforming ideas into intelligent digital solutions. As a startup-friendly IT consultancy and software development firm, we specialize in building scalable, reliable, and innovative technology that empowers businesses to thrive in the digital age. With a team of dedicated professionals and a customer-first approach, we deliver high-quality services across software development, web and mobile applications, and IT consulting. Whether you're a growing startup or an established enterprise, Duvee Technology is your trusted partner for smart, future-ready solutions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-6" data-anima="fade-right" data-time="1000">
                    <img src="../images/about.png" alt="Talent Acquisition" class="img-responsive">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
       
